-- EU Clears Swiss Post-La Poste International Mail Joint Venture
-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 2012-07-04T13:50:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-04/eu-clears-swiss-post-la-poste-international-mail-joint-venture.html
The European Commission gave
conditional approval to a bid by Swiss Post and  France ’s La
Poste to combine their cross-border mail activities.  The commission, the 27-nation European Union’s senior
antitrust regulator, said that Swiss Post had agreed to sell its
French subsidiary as a condition for permission to create a
joint venture for international mail delivery services.  The commission commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
 jbrunsden@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
